.music-recommend
  width: 100%
  height: 100%
  .slider-container
    height: 160px
    position: relative
    .slider-nav
      display: block
      width: 100%
      height: 100%
      .swiper-pagination-bullet-active
        background-color: #DDD
  .album-container
    .title
      height: 50px
      line-height: 50px
      text-align: center
      font-size: 15px
      font-weight: 400
    .album-list
      font-size: 15px
      padding-bottom: 20px
      .album-wrapper
        margin: 20px
        .left
          display: inline-block
          width: 60px
          height: 60px
          vertical-align: top
        .right
          display: inline-block
          max-width: 200px
          margin-left: 20px
          line-height: 20px
          .album-name, .singer-name, .public-time
            overflow: hidden
            text-overflow: ellipsis //text-overflow: clip|ellipsis|string;  1.修剪文本。2.显示省略符号来代表被修剪的文本。3.使用给定的字符串来代表被修剪的文本。
            white-space: nowrap  /*文本不会换行，文本会在在同一行上继续，直到遇到 <br> 标签为止*/
          .album-name
            font-weight: 500
      .album-wrapper:first-child
        margin-top: 0
      .album-wrapper:last-child
        margin-bottom: 0